  "description": {
    "zh": "我们浪费的时间已经够多了，再等下去 BTR 迟早会抛锚在路上。就在你去外头瞎晃悠，找些卡车轮子来糊弄我的时候，我认真做了点调查，找到了哪里可能有真正的军用负重轮。去军事储备基地，我要的轮子就在那里。 \n\n我要的是带轮毂的那种，而且尺寸也和 BTR 的一样。这次别再搞砸了，时限真的快要到了。",
    "en": "We've already lost time, but if we wait any longer, the BTR's gonna stall. While you were screwing around, I did some digging and found out where we can get some proper wheels. Go to the reserve military base, the wheels we need are there. \n\nThey come with rims attached, and they're a proper diameter for the BTR, too. Don't mess it up this time, the deadline's coming up."
